# Enum templates (from `enums.json`)

Summarizes **55** files: **`**/enums/**`** or **`*.enum.ts`** (see [`.agents/file-lists/enums.json`](../file-lists/enums.json)). Use enums as **keys for component maps** and discriminated unions (**`rules-typescript-clean-code.mdc`**, **`rules-bundle-react.mdc`**).

## Inventory snapshot

| Fact | Typical value |
| --- | --- |
| Extensions | `.ts` (~95%), tiny `.js` / `.tsx` |
| Path depth (median) | 4 segments |
| Common roots | `app/enums` (~45%), `app/services` (~33%), `app/pages` / `app/utils` / `app/wireframe` |

**Path examples:**

- `app/enums/DeviceOutput.enum.ts`
